sequenceDiagram
    participant App as "Flask app.py"
    participant Init as "init_* functions"
    participant State as "ServiceState (global)"
    participant FalkorDB as "FalkorDB"
    participant Qdrant as "Qdrant (optional)"
    
    App->>Init: init_falkordb()
    Init->>FalkorDB: Connect via FALKORDB_HOST:PORT
    alt Connection succeeds
        FalkorDB-->>State: state.memory_graph = graph
        State-->>App: Continue with graph
    else Connection fails
        FalkorDB-->>State: state.memory_graph = None
        State-->>App: Graceful degradation
    end
    
    App->>Init: init_qdrant()
    Init->>Qdrant: Connect via QDRANT_URL
    alt Qdrant configured
        Qdrant-->>State: state.qdrant = client
        State-->>App: Enable vector search
    else Qdrant unavailable
        Qdrant-->>State: state.qdrant = None
        State-->>App: Graph-only mode
    end
    
    Note over App,Qdrant: Graph-only mode: System continues<br/>with keyword + graph search